ortrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wickerbottom_Portrait.png/64px-Wickerbottom_Portrait.png?8c0f1f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Feather_Pencil\" title=\"Feather Pencil\"><img alt=\"Feather Pencil.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Feather_Pencil.png?51eb34\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Papyrus\" title=\"Papyrus\"><img alt=\"Papyrus.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Papyrus.png?5e1602\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lux_Aeterna\" title=\"Lux Aeterna\"><img alt=\"Lux Aeterna.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Lux_Aeterna.png?18e798\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><img alt=\"Interface arrow right.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Interface_arrow_right.png/42px-Interface_arrow_right.png?d3cbb3\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lux_Aeterna_Redux\" title=\"Lux Aeterna Redux\"><img alt=\"Lux Aeterna Redux.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Lux_Aeterna_Redux.png?471e7f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wickerbottom\" title=\"Wickerbottom\"><img alt=\"Wickerbottom Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wickerbottom_Portrait.png/64px-Wickerbottom_Portrait.png?8c0f1f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>The Feather Pencil was introduced to <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i> in <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/A_New_Reign#September_1st,_2016_-_A_Little_Fixer_Upper\" title=\"A New Reign\">A Little Fixer Upper</a></i> update during <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/A_New_Reign\" title=\"A New Reign\">A New Reign</a></i>. It was later introduced to <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve\">Don&#x27;t Starve</a></i> in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve/Version_History\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve/Version History\">Quality of Life</a></i> update.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:DST_Update_Fixxer-Upper.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Feather Pencil as seen in the poster for the A Little Fixer Upper update.\"><img alt=\"Feather Pencil as seen in the poster for the A Little Fixer Upper update.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/DST_Update_Fixxer-Upper.png/120px-DST_Update_Fixxer-Upper.png?ed0d39\" width=\"120\" height=\"68\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Feather Pencil as seen in the poster for the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/A_New_Reign#September_1,_2016_-_A_Little_Fixer_Upper\" title=\"A New Reign\">A Little Fixer Upper</a></i> update.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Dropped_Feather_Pencil.jpg\" class=\"image\" title=\"Feather Pencil on the ground.\"><img alt=\"Feather Pencil on the ground.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dropped_Feather_Pencil.jpg/87px-Dropped_Feather_Pencil.jpg?4f742c\" width=\"87\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Feather Pencil on the ground.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Cartographer%27s_Desk_and_Feather_Pencil.PNG\" class=\"image\" title=\"A Feather Pencil next to a Cartographer&#x27;s Desk.\"><img alt=\"A Feather Pencil next to a Cartographer&#x27;s Desk.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cartographer%27s_Desk_and_Feather_Pencil.PNG/99px-Cartographer%27s_Desk_and_Feather_Pencil.PNG?21af68\" width=\"99\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">A Feather Pencil next to a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cartographer%27s_Desk\" title=\"Cartographer&#x27;s Desk\">Cartographer&#x27;s Desk</a>.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul><div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Tools_and_Weapons-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Feather_Pencil/DST#Tools_and_Weapons-0\">Tools and Weapons</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Craftable_Items-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Feather_Pencil/DST#Craftable_Items-0\">Craftable Items</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><div></div>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"DST-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Feather_Pencil/DST#DST-0\">DST</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"DS-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Feather_Pencil/DST#DS-0\">DS</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"RoG-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Feather_Pencil/DST#RoG-0\">RoG</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"SW-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Feather_Pencil/DST#SW-0\">SW</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Ham-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Feather_Pencil/DST#Ham-0\">Ham</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n <p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
