  "plainText": "Don't Starve\nTogether\nFeather Pencil\n\"Yes, the feather IS necessary.\"\nObject Info\n15 sec.\nCan be Burned\n20\nCrafting\n×1 ×1 ×1\nFilters\nTier\nMiscellaneous\n\"featherpencil\"\n“The feather increases the scientific properties of the writing.”\n–Wilson\n“So what does the feather do again?”\n–Willow\n“Wolfgang must stick pinky out when holding it.”\n–Wolfgang\n“M...maybe I'll doodle something... When no one's looking.”\n–Wendy\n“WHY IS THE FEATHER SO APPEALING? EXPLAIN NOW, FLESHLINGS”\n–WX-78\n“Oh, how I missed proper writing implements!”\n–Wickerbottom\n“The bird murder wasn't even necessary. Heh.”\n–Woodie\n“Not as elegant as a quill and inkwell, but it'll do.”\n–Maxwell\n“A lightweight writing implement for use on signage.”\n–Wagstaff\n“Perhaps I'll pen a saga of my jöurneys!”\n–Wigfrid\n“Haha! It tickles!”\n–Webber\n“Lightweight. I like it.”\n–Walani\n“Lighter than my meringue.”\n–Warly\n“Fer makin' me mark.”\n–Woodlegs\n“WILBA CANST DRAWETH WITH A BIRDY THING”\n–Wilba\n“Picture drawer”\n–Wormwood\n“So good it even makes my handwriting legible!”\n–Wheeler\n“I've got ugly handwriting.”\n–Winona\n“Use this quill, I will, I will.”\n–Wortox\n“For fancy writing, florp.”\n–Wurt\n“I feel like I should write something poetic with this...”\n–Walter\n“Good for jotting down notes in a hurry.”\n–Wanda\nThe Feather Pencil is a craftable Item located in the Tools Tab. It requires a Science Machine to prototype and 1 Twigs, 1 Charcoal and 1 Jet Feather to craft. The Feather Pencil can be used to draw an Item on a Mini Sign, which breaks the pencil. The closest Item placed on the ground is what will be drawn on the Mini Sign when using a Feather Pencil.\nIn Don't Starve Together, the Feather Pencil can additionally be used to craft a Map Scroll and Wigfrid's Battle Songs.\nUsage[edit | edit source]\n×2\n×2\n×4\n×2\n×2\n×2\n×2\nTrivia[edit | edit source]\nThe Feather Pencil was introduced to Don't Starve Together in A Little Fixer Upper update during A New Reign. It was later introduced to Don't Starve in the Quality of Life update.\nGallery[edit | edit source]\nFeather Pencil as seen in the poster for the A Little Fixer Upper update.\nFeather Pencil on the ground.\nA Feather Pencil next to a Cartographer's Desk.\nTools and WeaponsCraftable Items\nView or edit this template\nDon't Starve Tools and Weapons\nEquipped Tools\nUnequipped Tools\nLight\nBooks\nCircuits\nBattle Calls\nWatches\nWeapons\nSlingshot Parts\nThrowables\nStaffs\nAmulets\nBackpacks\nClothing\nStage Costumes\nArmor\nDSTDSRoGSWHam\nView or edit this template\nDon't Starve Together Craftable Items\nRegular Filters\nSurvivor Items\nWilson\nWillow\nWolfgang\nWendy\nWX-78\nWickerbottom\nWoodie\nWes\nMaxwell\nWigfrid\nWebber\nWarly\nWortox\nWormwood\nWinona\nWurt\nWalter\nWanda\nTools\nLight Sources\nPrototypers & Stations\nRefined Materials\nWeapons\nArmor\nClothing\nHealing\nMagic\nDecorations\nStructures\nStorage Solutions\nCooking\nFood & Gardening\nFishing\nSeafaring\nBeefalo Riding\nWinter Items\nSummer Items\nRain Gear\nCrafting Station Filters\nSpecial Event\nAncient Pseudoscience\nCarpentry\nCartography\nCritters\nCelestial\nBrightsmithy\nShadowcraft\nFabrication\nBottle Exchange\nCombrining Filter\nTea Brewing Filter\nSculptures\nSeasonings\nTrading\nTrading Hutch\nOfferings\nCawnival Creation\nTrinket Trove\nMad Science\nWinter's Feast Cooking\nSanctum Smithy Filter\nCustom Course Shack Filter\nView or edit this template\nDon't Starve Craftable Items\nTools\nLight\nSurvival\nFood\nScience\nFight\nStructures\nRefine\nMagic\nDress\nAncient\nBooks\nTinkering\nView or edit this template\nDon't Starve: Reign of Giants Craftable Items\nTools\nLight\nSurvival\nFood\nScience\nFight\nStructures\nRefine\nMagic\nDress\nAncient\nBooks\nTinkering\nView or edit this template\nDon't Starve Shipwrecked and Volcano Craftable Items\nTools\nLight\nNautical\nSurvival\nFood\nScience\nFight\nStructures\nRefine\nMagic\nDress\nVolcanic\nBooks\nTinkering\nView or edit 