  "wikitext": "{{Navbutton/Separation}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|icon = Feather Pencil.png\n|image = Feather Pencil Dropped.png\n|burnTime = [[File:Light_Sources_Filter.png|32px|link=Fuel#Fire Fuel]] 15 sec.\n|canBeBurned=1\n|description = Yes, the feather IS necessary.\n|tier = 1\n|filter = {{Pic32|Tools Filter}} {{pic32|Decorations Filter}}\n|ingredient1 = Charcoal\n|multiplier1 = 1\n|ingredient2 = Jet Feather\n|multiplier2 = 1\n|ingredient3 = Twigs\n|multiplier3 = 1\n|stack = 20\n|spawnCode = \"featherpencil\"}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = The feather increases the scientific properties of the writing.\n|willow = So what does the feather do again?\n|wolfgang = Wolfgang must stick pinky out when holding it.\n|wendy = M...maybe I'll doodle something... When no one's looking.\n|wx78 = WHY IS THE FEATHER SO APPEALING? EXPLAIN NOW, FLESHLINGS\n|wickerbottom = Oh, how I missed proper writing implements!\n|woodie = The bird murder wasn't even necessary. Heh.\n|maxwell = Not as elegant as a quill and inkwell, but it'll do.\n|wagstaff = A lightweight writing implement for use on signage.\n|wigfrid = Perhaps I'll pen a saga of my jöurneys!\n|webber = Haha! It tickles!\n|walani = Lightweight. I like it.\n|warly = Lighter than my meringue.\n|woodlegs = Fer makin' me mark.\n|warbucks = A fine writing implement.\n|wilba = WILBA CANST DRAWETH WITH A BIRDY THING\n|wormwood = Picture drawer\n|wheeler = So good it even makes my handwriting legible!\n|winona = I've got ugly handwriting.\n|wortox = Use this quill, I will, I will.\n|wurt = For fancy writing, florp.\n|walter = I feel like I should write something poetic with this...\n|wanda = Good for jotting down notes in a hurry.\n|choose = wendy}}\nThe '''Feather Pencil''' is a craftable [[Item]] located in the [[Tools Tab]]. It requires a [[Science Machine]] to prototype and 1 [[Twigs]], 1 [[Charcoal]] and 1 [[Jet Feather]] to craft. The Feather Pencil can be used to draw an [[Item]] on a [[Mini Sign]], which breaks the pencil. The closest Item placed on the ground is what will be drawn on the Mini Sign when using a Feather Pencil.\n\nIn ''[[Don't Starve Together]]'', the Feather Pencil can additionally be used to craft a [[Map Scroll]] and [[Wigfrid|Wigfrid's]] [[Battle Songs]].\n\n=={{pic|32|Icon Tools}} Usage==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Feather Pencil\n|count1 = 1\n|item2 = Papyrus\n|count2 = 1\n|tool = Cartographer's Desk\n|result = Map Scroll}}\n{{Recipe\n|item4 = Log\n|count4 = 2\n|item3 = Twigs\n|count3 = 2\n|item2 = Gold Nugget\n|count2 = 1\n|item1 = Feather Pencil\n|count1 = 1\n|tool = Sawhorse\n|result = Pleasant Portrait}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Feather Pencil\n|item2 = Papyrus\n|item3 = Sewing Kit\n|result = Weaponized Warble\n|character = Wigfrid\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Feather Pencil\n|item2 = Papyrus\n|item3 = Life Giving Amulet\n|result = Heartrending Ballad\n|character = Wigfrid\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Feather Pencil\n|item2 = Papyrus\n|item3 = Moon Moth Wings\n|result = Clear Minded Cadenza\n|character = Wigfrid\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Feather Pencil\n|item2 = Papyrus\n|item3 = Thulecite Medallion\n|result = Bel Canto of Courage\n|character = Wigfrid\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Feather Pencil\n|item2 = Papyrus\n|item3 = Spittlefish\n|result = Fireproof Falsetto\n|character = Wigfrid\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Feather Pencil\n|item2 = Papyrus\n|item3 = Toma Root\n|result = Rude Interlude\n|character = Wigfrid\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Feather Pencil\n|item2 = Papyrus\n|item3 = Purple Gem\n|result = Startling Soliloquy\n|character = Wigfrid\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Feather Pencil\n|item2 = Papyrus\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Living Log\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Bookcase\n|character = Wickerbottom}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Feather Pencil\n|item2 = Papyrus\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Horticulture, Abridged\n|result = Horticulture, Expanded\n|character = Wickerbottom}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Feather Pencil\n|item2 = Papyrus\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = The End is Nigh\n|result = Pyrokinetics Explained\n|character = Wickerbottom}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Feather Pencil\n|item2 = Papyrus\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Lux Aeterna\n|result = Lux Aeterna Redux\n|character = Wickerbottom}}\n\n== {{pic|32|Placeholder}} Trivia ==\n* The Feather Pencil was introduced to ''[[Don't Starve Together]]'' in ''[[A New Reign#September 1st, 2016 - A Little Fixer Upper|A Little Fixer Upper]]'' update during ''[[A New Reign]]''. It was later introduced to ''[[Don't Starve]]'' in the ''[[Don't Starve/Version History|Quality of Life]]'' update.\n\n=={{Pic|32|Blueprint}} Gallery==\n<gallery captionalign=\"center\" hideaddbutton=\"true\">\nDST Update Fixxer-Upper.png|Feather Pencil as seen in the poster for the ''[[A New Reign#September 1, 2016 - A Little Fixer Upper|A Little Fixer Upper]]'' update.\nDropped Feather Pencil.jpg|Feather Pencil on the ground.\nCartographer's Desk and Feather Pencil.PNG|A Feather Pencil next to a [[Cartographer's Desk]].\n</gallery><tabber>\nTools and Weapons=\n{{Tools and Weapons}}\n|-|\nCraftable Items=\n{{Craftable Items|tool}}\n</tabber>\n\n[[es:Pluma Lápiz]]\n[[ko:깃펜]]\n[[Category:A New Reign]]\n[[Category:Tools Filter]]\n[[Category:Decorations Filter]]\n[[vi:Feather Pencil]]"
